Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=16}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.10,0:02:09.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Eu ouvi que uma ressaca\Nchamada Aqua Laguna está se aproximando!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.44,0:02:13.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yep! This town will be submerged\Nby midnight tonight! - OG}Isso! A cidade vai ficar submersa até meia-noite!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.49,0:02:15.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This shore will be totally submerged too! - OG}A costa vai ficar submersa também!{Z - CPS}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's terrible! We shouldn't stay around here! - OG}Que terrível! Temos que sair daqui!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! We shouldn't stay around here! - OG}Isso mesmo! Temos que sair daqui!{Z - Needs to match previous line}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:20.79,0:02:22.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'd better hurry up\Nand evacuate to high ground! - OG}Vamos evacuar para um lugar mais alto!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right!\NLet's hurry up and evacuate! - OG}Certo! Para o terreno mais alto!{Z - match again}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Evacuem! Evacuem!\N– Evacuem! Evacuem!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.13,0:02:31.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Evacuem! Evacuem!\N– Evacuem! Evacuem!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.73,0:02:44.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.52,0:02:51.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What were those voices just now...? - OG}Quem estava falando tudo aquilo agora...?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.36,0:02:54.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não esqueça de evacuar!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Evacua, Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.82,0:03:00.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles estavam falando\Nalgo sobre uma ressaca.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.85,0:03:02.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pensando bem...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.29,0:03:05.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o vento {\i1}está{\i0} muito forte mesmo.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.29,0:03:12.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me larga! Eu disse pra me largar!\NO que a gente fez?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't play innocent! You bastards are assassins! - OG}Não se faz de inocente, seus assassinos malditos!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.51,0:03:17.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How dare you shoot Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]?!\NWe won't let you get away! - OG}Como ousa atirar no Prefeito Iceburg!\NNão vamos deixar vocês escaparem!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.39,0:03:22.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Parem com isso, vocês!\NA gente tá dizendo que não fez nada!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.14,0:03:23.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.77,0:03:27.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{First off, Robin doesn't even have a reason to go after Iceburg-san, either! - OG}Pra começo de conversa, a Robin nem tem\Nmotivo pra ir atrás do prefeito!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.69,0:03:31.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just keep insisting that. - OG}{Keep telling yourself that. - Gaijin}Pode continuar repetindo isso até cansar.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.77,0:03:35.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, é o fim da linha pra vocês dois.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.74,0:03:42.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Learn that harming Iceburg-san, means that you're turning us, Galley-La Company, into an enemy... - OG}{By harming Mr. Iceburg, you're making\Nan enemy of both us, Galley-La Company... - JT}Ao atacar o Sr. Iceburg, vocês fizeram\Numa inimiga da Galley-La Company.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.29,0:03:49.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That you're turning this city,\NWater Seven, into an enemy. - OG}{and the whole city of Water Seven. - JT}E como resultado, isso significa\Na cidade inteira de Water Seven também.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.38,0:03:52.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why are you saying groundless things like that?! - OG}Por que vocês tão falando essas coisas absurdas?!{JT/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me deixa falar com o Icechefe!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desiste logo, pirata!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dá uma surra nele, Galley-La Company!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual é, Chapéu de Palha?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.66,0:04:26.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've only been defending.\NDon't you wanna fight back?! - OG}{You're only defending.\NDon't you wanna fight back?! - JT}{You just gonna defend,\Nor will you actually fight?! - Gaijin}Defender é tudo que você sabe fazer numa luta?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.83,0:04:30.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como eu já disse, eu não tenho\Nmotivo nenhum pra lutar com vocês!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.59,0:04:37.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We now know that pistols don't work on you. - OG}Agora sabemos que pistolas não funcionam contra você.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga. Parece que eles tão\Ntodos falando sério mesmo.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acertou em cheio!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não... ele escapou!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa foi por pouco...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Não consigo me mexer!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.42,0:05:37.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Pegaram ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.29,0:05:55.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso! Como se esperava do nosso\Norgulho, a Galley-La Company! Isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That feels great! - OG}Isso foi demais!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.13,0:06:00.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Right. A guy like that should be blown away! - OG}Isso mesmo. Um cara desses\Nmerece ser explodido!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ora, ora, ora...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.93,0:06:13.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But, you know, that Straw Hat shorty is the Franky Family's detestable enemy. - OG}Mas, sabe, aquele {\i1}Baixinho{\i0} de Palha é\No inimigo detestável da Família Franky.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.65,0:06:19.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu que estava lutando com ele primeiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.73,0:06:26.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't you come and snatch my prey when I'm fighting! - OG}{How dare you come along\Nand snatch my prey when I'm fighting?! - JT}Como vocês ousam vir aqui\Ne roubar minha presa?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.07,0:06:30.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quantas vezes eu tenho que\Nme repetir, seus desgraçados?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Galley-Laaa!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.66,0:06:39.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just hold on a sec. We'll deal\Nwith you after we capture him completely. - OG}Calma aí! A gente resolve com você\Ndepois que pegar esse aqui!{JT/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.00,0:06:44.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como eu já disse, por que diabos\Nvocês estão capturando a {\i1}minha{\i} presa?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.88,0:06:49.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, tanto faz. Parece que\Nvocês não entendem o que eu digo.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.60,0:06:50.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Paulie! Cuidado!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Galley-La! Corram!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.35,0:06:56.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Franky vai soltar um ataque insano!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? - OG}Hã?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.78,0:07:04.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Connector Set.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.37,0:07:10.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele derrubou um guindaste enorme\Ncom o mesmo ataque!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Derrubou um guindaste?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um canhão?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corram! Galley-La!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.92,0:07:19.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go! Get them, Bro! - OG}– Vai! Vai! Acaba com eles, Mano!\N– Vai! Vai! Acaba com eles, Mano!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.42,0:07:23.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, eu não vou atirar uma bala de canhão.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What I'll shoot out is an air bullet. - OG}O que eu vou disparar é uma bala de ar.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.68,0:07:30.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But its speed exceeds the speed of sound. - OG}Mas é mais rápida que a velocidade do som.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ar?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.98,0:07:36.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É perigoso! Corram!{OG}{Danger! Run! - JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Coup de Vent!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai... Que diabos foi aquilo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.46,0:08:42.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parecia que ventos de alta pressão\Nbateram na gente!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Outro guindaste está caindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.13,0:08:48.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Run! It'll reach this far! - OG}Corram! Vai cair pra esse lado!{JT/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá caindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso! Se lasquem!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.77,0:09:06.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A shipyard like this should be... crushed! - OG}Destruam esse estaleiro inteiro!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.54,0:09:26.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What is he?! A cyborg?\NWhere did he get that kind of technology? - OG}{He's supposed to be a cyborg?\NWhere did he get that kind of technology? - JT}Quem {\i1}é{\i0} esse cara?!\NComo ele conseguiu tecnologia de {\i1}ciborgue{\i0}?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E que canhão estranho foi aquele?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah... mas...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was able to escape thanks to that! - OG}{I'm free thanks to that. - JT}isso me ajudou a escapar!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami! Corre!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.85,0:09:36.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá bem?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No way I'd get brought down\Nby something like that! - OG}Algo assim não ia me derrubar!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Enfim, eu não entendo nada disso.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go see Iceboss somehow! - OG}A gente precisa ir falar com o Icechefe de qualquer jeito!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.74,0:09:54.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! We're going?!\NIt's not possible in this commotion!}O quê?! Vamos?!\NÉ impossível no meio dessa confusão!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, olha! O Chapéu de Palha tá fugindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, droga!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos ser cercados!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.71,0:10:02.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami...!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.12,0:10:02.90,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? - OG}Hã?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Segura firme!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.92,0:10:08.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, espera!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem eles escaparem!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.39,0:10:18.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles fugiram!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.48,0:10:19.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go after them! - OG}Atrás deles!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mano?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.10,0:10:30.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They got away.\NDon't you have to go after them? - OG}Eles fugiram. Você não vai atrás deles?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.73,0:10:35.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No... I ran outta fuel with\Nthe Coup de Vent I just shot. - OG}É... mas eu fiquei sem combustível\Nquando disparei o Coup de Vent.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look at my ducktail. - OG}Olha meu topete.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.92,0:10:41.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É... tá parecendo um salgueiro\Nbalançando ao vento.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.05,0:10:45.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqueles desgraçados ficaram no meu caminho.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.76,0:10:49.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Once I'm done refueling,\NI'll eliminate him for sure. - OG}Quando eu reabastecer,\Nvou acabar com ele de vez.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.71,0:10:56.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just as you'd expect from a man\Nwith a 100 million bounty on his head... He is a man of mettle. - OG}Ele faz jus à recompensa de 100 milhões...\NRealmente é um homem com fibra.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Seriously... - OG}Maldito seja!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Franky has really done it... - OG}O Franky fez um estrago e tanto...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.81,0:11:09.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What a terrible day today is! - OG}Esse dia não poderia ser pior...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.27,0:11:12.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At any rate,\Nwe can't let them get away. - OG}De qualquer forma, não podemos deixar eles escaparem.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.53,0:11:15.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Aqua Laguna vem essa noite.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.82,0:11:18.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Except for the two sea train departures left for today, - OG}Exceto pelas duas partidas restantes\Ndo Sea Train hoje,{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,eles não têm como sair dessa ilha.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Since they can no longer use\Nthe ship they came on. - OG}Ou seja, eles não podem mais usar\No navio em que vieram.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.19,0:11:27.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll gather information. - OG}Precisamos de mais informações.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.68,0:11:31.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Have every Galley-La craftsman\Nspread around the island. - OG}Espalhem todos os artesãos da Galley-La\Npela ilha.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.70,0:11:34.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(1460,2410,0.3,\alpha&HFF&)}Vamos resolver isso antes do pôr do sol!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.52,0:11:49.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vovó! Vovó! É Water Seven!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.70,0:11:55.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Be careful not to get too excited\Nand fall into the sea. - OG}Não fica tão empolgada a ponto de cair no mar.{JT/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.52,0:12:10.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That must be the Galley-La Company main office. - OG}Aquele deve ser o escritório principal da Galley-La Company.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está conectado ao Dock One.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.17,0:12:18.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{People who look like reporters are all over. - OG}{It looks like there are reporters... - JT}Parece que repórteres\Nse reuniram por toda parte.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.13,0:12:22.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shipwright-looking people are gathered there, too.}{and shipwrights gathered there. - JT}Parece que tem carpinteiros navais também.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.61,0:12:25.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]must be in that building. - OG}O Sr. Iceburg deve estar naquele prédio.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you serious about going? - OG}Você tem certeza disso?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.27,0:12:31.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Claro.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.73,0:12:36.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll go ask Iceboss in person\Nwhy he said Robin was one of the culprits. - OG}Vou perguntar pessoalmente pro Icechefe\Npor que ele tá dizendo que a Robin é uma das culpadas.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.94,0:12:42.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let me warn you. We're also being\Nchased after by the entire island! We can't do anything stupid. - OG}Só não esquece que a ilha inteira\Ntá atrás da gente! Nada de besteira.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.57,0:12:46.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenta descobrir antes onde\Nfica o quarto dele,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and seize an opportunity to carefully sneak in. - OG}e acha uma oportunidade pra se infiltrar.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.79,0:12:51.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza, eu tô indo.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.76,0:12:53.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.64,0:12:57.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They said they couldn't find them. - OG}Não conseguiram encontrá-los.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.59,0:12:59.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Hã?\N– Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.58,0:13:06.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é aquele?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ah... He is...! - OG}Ah... É o...!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The window got broken! - OG}{The window broke! - JT}Algo quebrou a janela!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.74,0:13:20.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{An attack! - OG}É um ataque!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.32,0:13:25.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Chapéu de Palha Luffy invadiu\No escritório principal!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! No meio do dia?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think that he attacks\Nthe main office again out of the blue! - OG}{To think he'd attack\Nthe main office again! - JT}{Not again at the main office so soon! - Z}{No way! He's already back at the main office?! - Gaijin}Atacar o escritório principal de novo tão rápido...?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde ele está?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.17,0:13:34.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He went to the mezzanine stairs to the third floor! - OG}Ele tá perto da escada pro terceiro andar!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde estão os encarregados?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.42,0:13:39.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're stationing craftsmen\Nall over the island, so they're all gone! - OG}Eles saíram pra posicionar os artesãos\Npela ilha! Só sobramos nós!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.02,0:13:43.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá usando um colete vermelho e um chapéu de palha!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.21,0:13:46.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Protect Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]! - OG}Protejam o Sr. Iceburg!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.21,0:13:49.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where did he go?! - OG}Onde ele foi?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cadê ele? Cadê ele?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Idiot! Don't shoot a pistol!\NWe're inside, remember? - OG}{Idiot! Don't shoot your pistol in here! - JT}Seu idiota! Não atira com pistola aqui dentro!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not good for Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]! - OG}Faz mal pro Sr. Iceburg!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry about the commotion\Noutside the room. - OG}Desculpa pela confusão lá fora.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.71,0:14:19.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom... o que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.81,0:14:23.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was told that Straw Hat Luffy\Nhas broken into this building. - OG}Me disseram que o Chapéu de Palha Luffy\Ninvadiu o prédio.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.93,0:14:29.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kalifa... tenho um favor a pedir.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ali está ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.15,0:14:34.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Caramba! Quanta gente!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá indo pro Prédio Dois!\NContornem por cima!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She is...! - OG}É ela!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kalifa-san, didn't a pirate come here? - OG}Senhorita Kalifa, algum pirata veio pra cá?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.21,0:15:03.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, não veio. Mais importante,\Npersigam ele com mais silêncio.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.82,0:15:06.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-san still needs to rest quietly. - OG}O Sr. Iceburg ainda está se recuperando.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpe.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.59,0:15:10.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Looks like the Straw Hat\Nhasn't reached this far yet. - OG}{Looks like Straw Hat\Nhasn't reached this far yet. - JT}Parece que o Chapéu de Palha ainda não chegou até aqui.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.57,0:15:11.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's stand watch around here. - OG}Vamos montar guarda aqui.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O alvo dele com certeza é esse quarto!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.30,0:15:29.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... you wanted to see me... right, pirate lad? - OG}Bom... você queria\Nme ver... certo, rapaz pirata?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.91,0:15:33.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É isso. Obrigado por me chamar\Npra dentro. Me salvou.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.69,0:15:38.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Duvido que você tenha vindo até aqui sozinho\Npra me matar no meio dessa confusão.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.19,0:15:40.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vim pra ouvir a verdade!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ontem à noite, eu vi Nico Robin\Ncom meus próprios olhos.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.55,0:15:51.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And... she is one of you. - OG}E... ela é da sua tripulação.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa é a verdade.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi mesmo a Robin?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não diga uma palavra.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.61,0:16:01.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Suas palavras não significam mais nada.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu te chamei aqui...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.32,0:16:07.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,porque tenho um favor a pedir.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.49,0:16:12.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let me see Nico Robin again now! - OG}Preciso que você me deixe ver a Nico Robin de novo!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.54,0:16:18.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chegamos! Chegamos!\NVovó Kokoro! Rápido! Rápido!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se empolga tanto.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Water Seven... Faz um tempo.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.72,0:16:30.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vovó! Rápido! Rápido!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom, tá bom.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.14,0:16:36.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wearing a mask is prohibited today\Nwhen you get on board the sea train. - OG}Hoje é proibido usar máscara\Nao embarcar no Sea Train.{JT/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.98,0:16:39.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, mostre seu bilhete e seu rosto.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is my own face! My own face! - OG}Essa {\i1}é{\i0} minha cara!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? - OG}Hã?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh! Kokoro-[/i1]san[/i0]! Hello! - OG}Oh! Dona Kokoro! Olá!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual é a confusão toda?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.74,0:16:54.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes... We're after the Straw Hats - OG}{Oh, we're hunting the Straw Hats. - JT}Ah, estamos caçando os que tentaram\Nassassinar o Sr. Iceburg.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{who're the culprits in Iceburg-san's attempted assassination. - OG}{Seems they're responsible for Mr. Iceburg's attempted assassination. - JT}Os culpados são os Chapéus de Palha.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg's assassination? Hm? - OG}Iceburg? Assassinato? Hm...?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.96,0:17:02.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi? Hm...?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essas pessoas...?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.67,0:17:12.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou repetir. Me deixe ver a Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's not possible. - OG}{I can't do that. - JT}Não dá agora.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente não sabe onde ela está.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tiros!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Veio do quarto!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]! - OG}Sr. Iceburg!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,V-Você tá bem...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I bet on a silly hope that I might be able to get closer to the truth. - OG}Apostei numa esperança boba de que\Npudesse chegar mais perto da verdade.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.42,0:17:55.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capturem todos os Chapéus de Palha!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com certeza!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.52,0:18:02.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.89,0:18:06.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{were you able to talk\Nto Iceburg-san by any chance? - OG}você conseguiu falar com o Sr. Iceburg?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.48,0:18:09.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Consegui. Ele disse que realmente viu a Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.65,0:18:13.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can't be...! Why would Robin\Ndo something like that? - OG}Não pode ser...! Por que a Robin\Nfaria algo assim?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.24,0:18:14.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu me recuso a acreditar nisso!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.22,0:18:37.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, bem-vindo.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yow! Como vai, Blueno?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.89,0:18:44.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá {\i1}super{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.86,0:18:48.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que estamos bem.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.61,0:18:52.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean, "I think"?!\NYou sure are an indecisive guy! - OG}Como assim, "acho"?!\NVocê é muito indeciso!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give me the usual! Fill them up! - OG}Me dá o de sempre! Enche tudo!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tem dinheiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só recarrega logo! Cola!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.79,0:19:06.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think that you run a bar with such a stingy notion that you take money from your customers...! - OG}Por que você administra um bar tão\Nsovino a ponto de cobrar dos clientes?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente tem dinheiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.92,0:19:10.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've got a million belly left over from shopping. - OG}Sobrou um milhão de berry das compras.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.34,0:19:11.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.55,0:19:14.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've got that much money from yesterday?! - OG}A gente tem tudo isso de\Ndinheiro sobrando de ontem?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que vergonha! Que coisa feia!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.47,0:19:19.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think that I didn't spend it all yesterday...! - OG}Não acredito que não gastei tudo ontem!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.39,0:19:20.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, give it to me! - OG}Me dá isso aqui!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.35,0:19:24.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yow! You guys! You're lucky! - OG}{Yow! You guys are lucky! - JT}Yow! Ei, vocês! Hoje é o dia de sorte de vocês!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.64,0:19:28.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All your alcohol is on me! - OG}Toda a bebida é por minha conta!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.31,0:19:31.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Drink as much as you like! - OG}Bebam à vontade!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.15,0:19:35.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whoa! That's our Franky! You're generous! - OG}Uau! Esse é o nosso Franky! Que generoso!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.20,0:19:39.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é o cara! O chefão do\Nsubmundo de Water Seven! Valeu!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Demais!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.58,0:19:43.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, there's more on the floor over there! - OG}Ei, tem mais ali!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.29,0:19:45.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Blueno! Cadê minha cola?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Anda logo!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:47.83,0:19:50.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que você tá se dando\Nbem, hein, Franky.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? - OG}Hã?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quê...?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.59,0:19:56.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Old hag Kokoro! That was you?! - OG}Kokoro, sua velha bruxa! Era você?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.05,0:20:00.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought it was a statue of a monster! - OG}{I thought you were a statue of a monster! - JT}Pensei que você fosse\Numa estátua de monstro!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.76,0:20:06.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, posso pedir mais um\Nrefresco, Franky?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.52,0:20:10.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a bar. It's not a place for kids! - OG}Isso aqui é um bar. Não é lugar pra criança!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're doing well, right? - OG}Você tá bem, né?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.07,0:20:15.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?! Tá bom então. Faça como quiser.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Suco!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.82,0:20:21.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, I'm doing well,\Nbut I'm feeling gloomy. I feel terrible. - OG}É, eu tô bem, mas tô de mau humor.\NMe sinto péssimo.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.95,0:20:26.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me sinto péssimo essa semana toda,\Ngraças àquele pirata maldito!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Here's the refilled cola! Thanks for waiting! - OG}Tudo cheio! Desculpa a demora!{JT/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Até que enfim!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.92,0:20:33.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Combustível! Combustível!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.34,0:20:40.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Here it comes! Here it comes! Oh, yeah! - OG}Lá vem. Lá vem. Lá vem!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.60,0:20:55.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've revived! That jerk!\NNext time I see him, I'll beat him up! - OG}Revivi! Da próxima vez\Nque eu ver aquele desgraçado, ele tá ferrado!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A propósito, velha bruxa, por que você tá aqui?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.78,0:21:00.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Aqua Laguna está vindo.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.41,0:21:05.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é? Com razão\No vento está tão forte.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.04,0:21:07.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você já preparou sua casa?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.91,0:21:10.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, my house is gone. - OG}Que nada! Minha casa já era.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.50,0:21:13.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tenho nada que possa afundar,\Nentão não me preocupo.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:19.13,0:21:23.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu ia tomar uma com o Iceburg,\Nmas fiquei sabendo que ele levou um tiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, sounds like it. - OG}É, foi o que eu ouvi também.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.47,0:21:29.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They say it was the pirates' doing. Galley-La and the townspeople \Nare furious right now. - OG}Dizem que foram os piratas.\NA Galley-La e o povo estão furiosos.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.89,0:21:33.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Pirates' doing? - OG}Piratas fizeram isso?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.48,0:21:36.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você realmente acha que foi isso?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.32,0:21:38.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que você sabe de algo.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't say whatever comes to mind, old hag. - OG}Não fala o que te dá na telha, sua velha bruxa.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.57,0:21:45.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg has been getting nagged all this time\Nby the World Government, right? - OG}O Governo Mundial anda enchendo o saco\Ndo Iceburg faz tempo.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.28,0:21:50.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Então o quê? Você tá dizendo que\Naquele oficial, Corgi, fez isso?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.62,0:21:53.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That tubby isn't an assassin type! - OG}Aquele gordinho não tem cara de assassino!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.63,0:21:58.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No... Shadowy incidents are the work of CP9. - OG}Não... operações secretas são trabalho do CP9.{JT/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você sabe sobre isso, Blueno?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:01.17,0:22:02.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só ouvi alguns rumores.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:02.63,0:22:08.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Geez... Common folk sure do like to believe\Nrumors of things like nonexistent organizations. - OG}Ah, por favor. O povo adora acreditar em qualquer\Nboato sobre organizações secretas.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How foolish... It does exist. - OG}Que bobagem... Essa realmente existe.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:11.27,0:22:17.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But they never show themselves, since their unit works secretly in the shadows. - OG}Mas eles nunca se mostram,\Njá que são uma unidade secreta que age nas sombras.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.20,0:22:26.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De onde vem essa confiança toda?\NVocê sabe de alguma coisa?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:28.03,0:22:31.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard about it over there. - OG}Ouvi falar de um cara por aí.{Gaijin - Diverges from the Japanese, but captures the spirit of the line better in English}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.08,0:22:33.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, isso é só um boato então!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:33.00,0:22:34.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vem com–
Dialogue: 5,0:22:34.92,0:22:38.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It always being a rumor is the scary part. - OG}O assustador é que é {\i1}sempre{\i0} um boato.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:39.13,0:22:42.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles eliminam pessoas sem ninguém perceber.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:42.51,0:22:45.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se você se meter com eles, é homem morto.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:52.48,0:22:57.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigada. O trabalho que tínhamos\Nque fazer ontem saiu bem.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:57.11,0:22:59.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:03.82,0:23:05.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi moleza.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:05.53,0:23:10.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Although naturally you're now\Nbeing pursued by the whole town. - OG}Claro. Embora, agora você esteja\Nsendo perseguida pela cidade inteira.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:10.49,0:23:12.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:12.25,0:23:15.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas isso é temporário.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:15.00,0:23:18.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O importante é... hoje à noite.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos infiltrar na residência\Ndo Iceburg mais uma vez.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:22.26,0:23:27.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If worse comes to worst,\Nit's okay to eliminate all the evidence. - OG}Na pior das hipóteses,\Nnão me importo em eliminar todas as evidências.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:28.05,0:23:35.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Among the disciples of this Tom guy who originally had it, Iceburg is the only one currently alive. - OG}Tom tinha originalmente... e de seus discípulos,\NIceburg é o único vivo hoje.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:35.44,0:23:38.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não importa o quanto ele finja inocência,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:38.27,0:23:42.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{in the name of CP9,\Nwe'll take it away tonight for sure. - OG}{in the name of CP9,\Nwe'll take it away for sure tonight. - JT}em nome do CP9, com certeza vamos tomar dele essa noite.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:43.03,0:23:47.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lembrem-se de que essa é uma missão pela justiça.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=17}===============================DIALOGUE============================
